# This directory is generated by Mockly during build so AI agents can discover the bundled skill.
# Keep this .gitignore checked in so the generated SKILL.md stays out of source control
# and updates to Mockly don't cause unnecessary changes to your repository.
# To disable the generation of the SKILL.md file, set <MocklySkill>false</MocklySkill> in your project or Directory.Build.props.
*
!.gitignore
